Package au.aklein.metajava.internal

Contains the au.aklein.metajava.internal classes for the reading and parsing of class files.

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    AttributeInfo<VisitorType extends AttributeVisitor,ReturnType>
    Attribute, used to store data relating to ClassFileReader, FieldMethodInfo and CodeAttribute structures.
    ClassFile
    A service provider interface for classes which read and parse class files.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AnnotationAttribute
    Holds the attribute information for annotation
    AnnotationData
    Holds the data for a given annotation in an AnnotationAttribute
    AttributeVisitor
    Process an attribute to obtain relevant information
    ClassAttributeVisitor
    Process a class attribute to obtain relevant information
    ClassFileReader
    Handles the file IO and parsing of .class files
    CodeAttribute
    Holds the attribute information containing the instructions and auxiliary information for a single method
    CodeAttributeVisitor
    Process a code attribute to obtain relevant information
    Constant<T>
    Holds data for a single literal entry in a class' constant pool
    ConstantPoolEntry<T,U>
    Holds data for a single reference type entry in a class' constant pool
    DefaultAttribute
    Default attribute class, used for attributes which are not otherwise handled.
    ElementValue
    A representation of the element_value structure - used to describe element values in annotation attributes.
    FieldAttributeVisitor
    Process a field_info attribute to obtain relevant information
    FieldMethodInfo
    A class representing both the field_info and method_info data structures.
    InnerClassAttribute
    Holds the attribute information containing all of the InnerClassData entries within a class.
    InnerClassData
    Holds the attribute information of a single inner class.
    MethodAttributeVisitor
    Process a method_info attribute to obtain relevant information
    ParameterAnnotationAttribute
    Holds the attribute information for a parameter annotation.
    PathProvider
    Obtain a list of paths to .class files in directories and JAR files
    SignatureAttribute
    Holds the attribute information for "generic signature information for any class, interface, constructor or member whose generic signature in the Java programming language would include references to type variables or parameterized types."
